    <MetaDataItem name="Description">ZP 3102 Z-Wave Motion Sensor
(Temperature Sensor Build-In)
 
Features:
* Passive Infrared Sensor (PIR)
* 2~10 meter Motion Range 
* 120 Degree Horizontal Angle Coverage
* Temperature Function
* Low battery detection
* Panasonic CR123A Battery
* Tamper Switch
* 100ft line of sight
* LED Status Indicator
* Operating temp: -15oC~40oC
* Working Voltage: 3V
* Dimensions: 84*62*50mm
* Frequency Available: US/EU/JP/IN/BR Version Available
* On Japan Telec Certification Process
* Taiwan NCC Approved
